Welcome
--------
This repo contains graph implementations in the following languages :
   1. C++
   2. C
   3. Cuda(Soon)
   4. Java(Soon)

Following are the implementations :
   1. Adjacency Lists Represantation
   2. Adjacency Matrix Representation
   3. Breadth-First Search with equiweighted edges and using (1)
   4. Depth-First Search with equiweighed edges and using (1)
   5. Topological-Sort of dag (directed acyclic graph)using (4) and (5)
   6. Finding Strongly Connected Components of a directed graph using (4)
   7. Data-Structure for Dis-Joint Sets used in (8)
   8. Kruskal algorithm to find minimum spanning tree using (7)
   9. Prim Algorithm (Under Implementation)
   10. Bellman-Ford Algorithm to find shortest path of weighted graphs